Hey, this is my first map so go easy. :)

Just got bored and made it up as i went along so its abit random. The whole thing took me about 40mins to make so its pretty basic. 

Overall its a quite fun map for a few rounds but it does have a problem getting to the top of the struture requires the player to swin a long distance underwater, you can make it with about 60  health remaining or even 100 if you manage to get a breath going up.
